title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 753-4.4 - Receiving notices
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 753-4.4 - Receiving notices

State Regulations

Each operator shall establish a means of receiving
notices of planned excavation or demolition from the one-call notification
system in accordance with the procedures of the system. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16
§§
753-4.4

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
